quran[1606]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,(q) sabaq alkalam ealaa alhrwf almqttaet fi 'awal surat albqr. 'uqsim allah taealaa bialquran alkarim dhi almjd walshrf
  50,2,"bal ejb almukadhibun llrswl salaa allah ealayh wasalam 'an ja'ahum mundhir minhum yndhrhm eiqab allh, faqal alkafirun biallah wrswlh: hdha shay' mstghrb ytejb mnh"
  50,3,"a'idha mitna wsirna trabana, kayf yumkin alrujue baed dhlk 'iilaa ma kunna elyh? dhlk raje baeid alwqwe"
  50,4,"qd ealimna ma tanqus al'ard wtufny min ajsamhm, waeindana kitab mahfuz min altaghyir waltbdyl, bikuli ma yajri ealayhim fi hayatihim wabaed mmathm"
  50,5,"bl kdhdhab hwla' almushrikun bialquran hin ja'hm, fahum fi 'amr mdtrb mkhtlt, la ythbtwn ealaa shy', wala ystqr lahum qrar"
  50,6,"aghafalu hin kafaruu balbeth, falam yanzuruu 'iilaa alsama' fwqhm, kayf banaynaha mstwyt alarja', thabitat albna', wazayanaaha balnjwm, wama laha min shqwq wftwq, fahi salimat min altfawt waleywb?"
  50,7,"walard wssaenaha wfrshnaha, wajaealna fiha jbala thwabt; lialaa tmyl bahlha, wa'anbatna fiha min kuli nawe hasan almanzar nafe, yasurr wybhj alnazr 'ilyh"
  50,8,"khlq allah alsmwat wal'ard wama fihima min alayat aleazimat eibratan yutbsr biha min eamana aljhl, wdhkra likuli eabd khade khayf wajil, rjjae 'iilaa allah eaza wjl"
  50,9,"wnzzalna min alsama' mtrana kthyr almnafe, fa'anbatna bih basatin kathirat alashjar, wahaba alzare almhswd"
  50,10,wanbtna alnakhl tiwala laha tale mtrakb baedah fawq bedin
  50,11,"anbtna dhlk rzqana lileibad yqtatwn bih hsb hajathm, wa'ahyayna bhdha alma' aladhi 'anzalnah min alsama' baldat qad ajdbt wqhtt, fala zare fiha wala nbat, kama ahyyna bdhlk alma' al'ard almaytat nukhrijukum yawm alqiamat 'ahya' baed almwt"
  50,12,"kdhdhabt qabl hwla' almushrikin min quraysh qwm nuh wa'ashab albyr wthmwd, waead wafireawn waqawm lwt, wa'ashab al'aykat qwm sheyb, waqawm tubbae alhimyary, kl hwla' alaqwam kdhdhabu rslhm, fahaqa ealayhim alwaeid aldhy twedhm allah bih ealaa kfrhm"
  50,13,"kdhdhabt qabl hwla' almushrikin min quraysh qwm nuh wa'ashab albyr wthmwd, waead wafireawn waqawm lwt, wa'ashab al'aykat qwm sheyb, waqawm tubbae alhimyary, kl hwla' alaqwam kdhdhabu rslhm, fahaqa ealayhim alwaeid aldhy twedhm allah bih ealaa kfrhm"
  50,14,"kdhdhabt qabl hwla' almushrikin min quraysh qwm nuh wa'ashab albyr wthmwd, waead wafireawn waqawm lwt, wa'ashab al'aykat qwm sheyb, waqawm tubbae alhimyary, kl hwla' alaqwam kdhdhabu rslhm, fahaqa ealayhim alwaeid aldhy twedhm allah bih ealaa kfrhm"
  50,15,"afaeajazna ean abtdae alkhalq al'awal aldhy khalaqnah walam yakun shyyana, fnejz ean 'ieadthm khlqana jdydana baed fnayhm? la yejzna dhlk, bal nahn ealayh qadrwn, wlknhm fi hayrt washk min 'amr albaeth walnshwr"
  50,16,"wlqd khalaqna al'insan, wanaelam ma tuhaddith bih nfsh, wanahn 'aqrab 'iilayh min habl alwarid (whw eirq fi alenq mutasil balqlb)"
  50,17,"hyn yaktub almalakan almtrsdan ean ymynh waean shmalh aemalh. faldhy ean alyamin yaktub alhsnat, waladhi ean alshamal yaktub alsyyat"
  50,18,"ma yalfiz min qawl fytklm bih 'iilaa ladayh malak yrqb qwlh, wyktbh, wahu malak hadr mueadd ldhlk"
  50,19,"wja't shdt almawt wghamrth bialhaqi aldhy laa mrdd lah wala mnas, dhlk ma kunt minh - 'ayuha al'iinsan - tahrub wtrwgh"
  50,20,"wnufkh fi \"alqrn\" nafkhat albaeth althanyt, dhlk alnfkh fi yawm wuque alwaeid aldhy tweead allah bih alkfar"
  50,21,"wja't kulu nafs maeaha malakan, 'ahaduhuma yswqha 'iilaa almhshr, walakhar yashhad ealayha bima eamilat fi aldunya min khayr wshr"
  50,22,"lqd kunt fi ghaflat min hdha aldhy eaynt alyawm 'ayuha al'insan, fakashafna eank ghita'ak aldhy ghtta qlbk, fzalt alghflt enk, fabasaruk alyawm fima tashhad qawiin shdyd"
  50,23,"wqal almalak alkatib alshahid elyh: hdha ma eindi min diwan emlh, wahu ldy mueadd mahfuz hadr"
  50,24,"yaqul allah llmalakyn alssayiq walshhyd baed 'an yafsil bayn alkhlayq: 'alqia fi jahanam kula jahd 'ana allah hu al'ilh alhqqu, kthyr alkufr waltkdhyb meand llhq, mnnae li'ada' ma ealayh min alhuquq fi malh, muetd ealaa eibad allah waealaa hdwdh, shakk fi waedah wweydh, aldhy 'ushrik ballh, febd maeah mebwdana akhar min khlqh, fa'alqiah fi eadhab jahanam alshdyd"
  50,25,"yqwl allah llmalakyn alssayiq walshhyd baed 'an yafsil bayn alkhlayq: 'alqia fi jahanam kula jahd 'ana allah hu al'ilh alhqqu, kthyr alkufr waltkdhyb meand llhq, mnnae li'ada' ma ealayh min alhuquq fi malh, muetd ealaa eibad allah waealaa hdwdh, shakk fi waedah wweydh, aldhy 'ushrik ballh, febd maeah mebwdana akhar min khlqh, fa'alqiah fi eadhab jahanam alshdyd"
  50,26,"yqwl allah llmalakyn alssayiq walshhyd baed 'an yafsil bayn alkhlayq: 'alqia fi jahanam kula jahd 'ana allah hu al'ilh alhqqu, kthyr alkufr waltkdhyb meand llhq, mnnae li'ada' ma ealayh min alhuquq fi malh, muetd ealaa eibad allah waealaa hdwdh, shakk fi waedah wweydh, aldhy 'ushrik ballh, febd maeah mebwdana akhar min khlqh, fa'alqiah fi eadhab jahanam alshdyd"
  50,27,"qal shytanh aldhy kan maeah fi aldnya: rabina ma adllth, wlkn kan fi tariq baeid ean sabil alhda"
  50,28,"qal allah teala: la takhtasimuu ldy alyawm fi mawqif aljaza' walhsab; 'iidh la fayidatan min dhlk, waqad qaddamt 'iilaykum fi aldunya bialwaeid liman kafar bi wesany"
  50,29,"ma yughyar alqawl ldya, walast aedhdhib ahdana bdhnb ahd, fala aedhdhib ahdana 'iilaa bidhanbih baed qiam alhujat elyh"
  50,30,"adhkr -ayha alrswl- lqwmk yawm naqul lijahanam yawm alqyamt: hal amtlat? wataqul jhnm: hal min ziadat min aljini wal'ins? fyde alrb -jl jlalh- qadamah fyha, fynzwy bedha ealaa bed, wtqwl: qt, qt"
  50,31,"wqurribt aljanat lilmutaqin mkanana ghayr baeid mnhm, fahum yshahdwnha ziadat fi almsrrat lhm"
  50,32,"yqal lhm: hdha aladhi kuntum tueadun bih - 'ayuha almutaqun - likuli tayb min dhnwbh, hafiz likuli ma qarrabh 'iilaa rbh, min alfrayd waltaeat, man khaf allah fi aldunya wlqyh yawm alqiamat biqalb tayb min dhnwbh"
  50,33,"yqal lhm: hdha aladhi kuntum tueadun bih - 'ayuha almutaqun - likuli tayb min dhnwbh, hafiz likuli ma qarrabh 'iilaa rbh, min alfrayd waltaeat, man khaf allah fi aldunya wlqyh yawm alqiamat biqalb tayb min dhnwbh"
  50,34,"wyqal lhwla' almwmnyn: adkhuluu aljanat dkhwla mqrwnana balslamt min alafat walshrwr, mamwnana fih jmye almkarh, dhlk hu yawm alkhulud bila anqtae"
  50,35,"lhwla' almuminin fi aljanat ma yrydwn, waladayna ealaa ma aetynahm ziadat neym, aezamuh alnazar 'iilaa wajh allah alkrym"
  50,36,"wahlkna qabl hwla' almushrikin min quraysh ammana kthyrt, kanuu 'ashada minhum quatan wstwt, ftwwafu fi albilad wemmaru wdmmaru fyha, hal min mahrab min eadhab allah hin ja'hm?"
  50,37,"'in fi 'ihlak alqurun almadiat laeibratan liman kan lah qalb yaeqil bh, 'aw asgha alsme, wahu hadr bqlbh, ghyr ghafl wala sahin"
  50,38,"wlqd khalaqna alsmwat alsabe wal'ard wama baynahuma min asnaf almkhlwqat fi stt ayam, wama asabna min dhlk alkhalq teb wala nasab. wafi hadhih alqudrat aleazimat dalil ealaa qudratih -sbhanh - ealaa 'iihya' almawtaa min bab awla"
  50,39,"fasbr -ayha alrswl- ealaa ma yaquluh almkdhbwn, fa'iina allah lahum balmrsad, wsll lirabik hamdana lah salat alsubh qabl tulue alshams wslat aleasr qabl alghrwb, wsll min allyl, wsbbih bihamd rabik eaqib alslwat"
  50,40,"fasbr -ayha alrswl- ealaa ma yaquluh almkdhbwn, fa'iina allah lahum balmrsad, wsll lirabik hamdana lah salat alsubh qabl tulue alshams wslat aleasr qabl alghrwb, wsll min allyl, wsbbih bihamd rabik eaqib alslwat"
  50,41,"waistamae -ayha alrswl- yawm yunadi almalak bnfkhh fi \"alqrn\" min makan qryb, yawm yasmaeun sayhatan albaeth bialhaqi aldhy la shaka fih wala amtra', dhlk yawm khuruj 'ahl alqubur min qbwrhm"
  50,42,"wastme -ayha alrswl- yawm yunadi almalak bnfkhh fi \"alqrn\" min makan qryb, yawm yasmaeun sayhatan albaeth bialhaqi aldhy la shaka fih wala amtra', dhlk yawm khuruj 'ahl alqubur min qbwrhm"
  50,43,"'inna nahn nuhyi alkhalq wnmythm fi aldnya, wa'iilayna masirihim jmyeana yawm alqiamat llhsab waljza', yawm ttsde al'ard ean almawtaa almqbwryn bha, fykhrjwn msreyn 'iilaa aldaey, dhlk aljame fi mawqif alhisab ealayna sahl ysyr"
  50,44,"'inna nahn nuhyi alkhalq wnmythm fi aldnya, wa'iilayna masirihim jmyeana yawm alqiamat llhsab waljza', yawm ttsde al'ard ean almawtaa almqbwryn bha, fykhrjwn msreyn 'iilaa aldaey, dhlk aljame fi mawqif alhisab ealayna sahl ysyr"
  50,45,"nhn 'aelam bima yaqul hwla' almushrikun min aftira'an ealaa allah wtkdhyb bayath, wama 'ant -ayha alrswl- ealayhim bmsllat; ltjbrhm ealaa al'islam, wa'iinama bueitht mbllighana, fdhkkir bialquran man yakhshaa weydy; li'ana man la yakhaf alwaeid la ydhdhakr"
  51,1,"aqsm allah taealaa balryah almthyrat lltrab, falshb alhamlat thqla ezymana min alma', falsfn alty tajri fi albahhar jryana dha yasr wshwlt, falmlaykt alty tuqassim 'amr allah fi khlqh. 'iina aladhi tueadun bh- 'ayuha alnas- min albaeth walhisab lkayn haqa yqyn, wa'iin alhisab walthwab ealaa al'aemal lkayn la mhalt"
  51,2,"aqsm allah taealaa balryah almthyrat lltrab, falshb alhamlat thqla ezymana min alma', falsfn alty tajri fi albahhar jryana dha yasr wshwlt, falmlaykt alty tuqassim 'amr allah fi khlqh. 'iina aladhi tueadun bh- 'ayuha alnas- min albaeth walhisab lkayn haqa yqyn, wa'iin alhisab walthwab ealaa al'aemal lkayn la mhalt"
  51,3,"'uqsim allah taealaa balryah almthyrat lltrab, falshb alhamlat thqla ezymana min alma', falsfn alty tajri fi albahhar jryana dha yasr wshwlt, falmlaykt alty tuqassim 'amr allah fi khlqh. 'iina aladhi tueadun bh- 'ayuha alnas- min albaeth walhisab lkayn haqa yqyn, wa'iin alhisab walthwab ealaa al'aemal lkayn la mhalt"
  51,4,"aqsm allah taealaa balryah almthyrat lltrab, falshb alhamlat thqla ezymana min alma', falsfn alty tajri fi albahhar jryana dha yasr wshwlt, falmlaykt alty tuqassim 'amr allah fi khlqh. 'iina aladhi tueadun bh- 'ayuha alnas- min albaeth walhisab lkayn haqa yqyn, wa'iin alhisab walthwab ealaa al'aemal lkayn la mhalt"
  51,5,"aqsm allah taealaa balryah almthyrat lltrab, falshb alhamlat thqla ezymana min alma', falsfn alty tajri fi albahhar jryana dha yasr wshwlt, falmlaykt alty tuqassim 'amr allah fi khlqh. 'iina aladhi tueadun bh- 'ayuha alnas- min albaeth walhisab lkayn haqa yqyn, wa'iin alhisab walthwab ealaa al'aemal lkayn la mhalt"
  51,6,"aqsm allah taealaa balryah almthyrat lltrab, falshb alhamlat thqla ezymana min alma', falsfn alty tajri fi albahhar jryana dha yasr wshwlt, falmlaykt alty tuqassim 'amr allah fi khlqh. 'iina aladhi tueadun bh- 'ayuha alnas- min albaeth walhisab lkayn haqa yqyn, wa'iin alhisab walthwab ealaa al'aemal lkayn la mhalt"
  51,7,"waqsm allah taealaa balsma' dhat alkhalq alhsn, 'inkm- 'ayuha almkdhbwn- lafi qawl mdtrb fi hadha alqran, wafi alrasul salaa allah ealayh wslm. yusrf ean alquran walrasul salaa allah ealayh wasalam man surf ean al'iiman bhma; l'ieradh ean 'adilat allah wbrahynh alyqynyt falam ywffaq 'iilaa alkhyr"
  51,8,"waqsm allah taealaa balsma' dhat alkhalq alhsn, 'inkm- 'ayuha almkdhbwn- lafi qawl mdtrb fi hadha alqran, wafi alrasul salaa allah ealayh wslm. yusrf ean alquran walrasul salaa allah ealayh wasalam man surf ean al'iiman bhma; l'ieradh ean 'adilat allah wbrahynh alyqynyt falam ywffaq 'iilaa alkhyr"
  51,9,"waqsm allah taealaa balsma' dhat alkhalq alhsn, 'inkm- 'ayuha almkdhbwn- lafi qawl mdtrb fi hadha alqran, wafi alrasul salaa allah ealayh wslm. yusrf ean alquran walrasul salaa allah ealayh wasalam man surf ean al'iiman bhma; l'ieradh ean 'adilat allah wbrahynh alyqynyt falam ywffaq 'iilaa alkhyr"
  51,10,"luein alkdhabwn alzanwn ghyr alhq, aladhin hum fi lujjat min alkufr waldlalt ghafilun mtmadwn"
  51,11,"luein alkdhabwn alzanwn ghyr alhq, aladhin hum fi lujjat min alkufr waldlalt ghafilun mtmadwn"
  51,12,"ysal hwla' alkdhabwn sual aistibead wtkdhyb: mataa yawm alhisab waljza'?"
  51,13,"ywm aljza', yawm yuedhdhabwn bal'ihraq balnar, wyqal lhm: dhuquu edhabkm aladhi kuntum bih tastaejilun fi aldnya"
  51,14,"ywm aljza', yawm yuedhdhabwn bal'ihraq balnar, wyqal lhm: dhuquu edhabkm aladhi kuntum bih tastaejilun fi aldnya"
  51,15,"'in aladhin ataqawa allah fi janaat ezymt, waeuyun ma'an jaryt, aetahm allah jmye munahm min asnaf alneym, fakhdhu dhlk radyn bh, fariht bih nfwshm, 'iinahum kanuu qabl dhlk alnaeim muhsinin fi aldunya baemalhm alsalht"
  51,16,"'in aladhin ataqawa allah fi janaat ezymt, waeuyun ma'an jaryt, aetahm allah jmye munahm min asnaf alneym, fakhdhu dhlk radyn bh, fariht bih nfwshm, 'iinahum kanuu qabl dhlk alnaeim muhsinin fi aldunya baemalhm alsalht"
  51,17,"kan hwla' almhsnwn qalilana min allayl ma ynamwn, yusallun lirabihim qanitin lh, wafi 'awakhir allayl qubayl alfajr yastaghfirun allah min dhnwbhm"
  51,18,"kan hwla' almhsnwn qalilana min allayl ma ynamwn, yusallun lirabihim qanitin lh, wafi 'awakhir allayl qubayl alfajr yastaghfirun allah min dhnwbhm"
  51,19,"wfy 'amwalihim haqun wajib wmsthb llmhtajyn aladhin yas'alun alnas, waladhin la ysalwnhm hya'"
  51,20,"wfy al'ard eabr wdlayl wadihatan ealaa qudrat khalaqaha li'ahl alyaqin bi'ana allah hu al'ilh alhaqu wahdah la sharik lh, walmsddiqyn larasuluh salaa allah ealayh wslm"
  51,21,"wfy khalaq 'anfusakum dalayil ealaa qudrat allah teala, waeabr tdlkm ealaa whdanyt khalqkm, wa'anah la 'ilh lakum yastahiqu alebadt swah, aghafaltm enha, fala tubsirun dhlk, ftetbrwn bh?"
  51,22,"wfy alsama' rizqukum wama tueadun min alkhayr walshr walthwab waleqab, waghayr dhlk klh maktub mqddar"
  51,23,"aqsm allah taealaa binafsih alkarimat ann ma waeadakum bih hq, fala tashukku fih kama la tashukkun fi ntqkm"
  51,24,"hl 'atak -ayha alrswl- hadith dayf 'iibrahim aladhin akrmhm- wakanuu min almalayikat alkram- hin dakhaluu ealayh fi byth, fhyawh qaylyn lh: slamana, frdd ealayhim altahiat qayla salam elykm, 'antum qawm ghrba' la nerfkm"
  51,25,"hl 'atak -ayha alrswl- hadith dayf 'iibrahim aladhin akrmhm- wakanuu min almalayikat alkram- hin dakhaluu ealayh fi byth, fhyawh qaylyn lh: slamana, frdd ealayhim altahiat qayla salam elykm, 'antum qawm ghrba' la nerfkm"
  51,26,"feadal wmal khafiat 'iilaa ahlh, femd 'iilaa eajal samin fdhbhh, wshwah balnar, thuma wadeah amamhm, wtllatf fi daeawtuhum 'iilaa altaeam qayla 'alaa taklwn?"
  51,27,"feadal wmal khafiat 'iilaa ahlh, femd 'iilaa eajal samin fdhbhh, wshwah balnar, thuma wadeah amamhm, wtllatf fi daeawtuhum 'iilaa altaeam qayla 'alaa taklwn?"
  51,28,"flma rahm laa yakulun ahss fi nafsih khwfana mnhm, qaluu lh: la takhaf 'iinaa rusul allh, wabasharuh bi'ana zawjatih \"sarata\" stld lah wldana, sayakun min 'ahl aleilm biallah wbdynh, wahu 'iishaq ealayh alslam"
  51,29,"falamaa samieat zawjat 'iibrahim mqalt hwla' almalayikat balbshart aqblt nahwahum fi syht, fltmt wajahaha tejbana mn hdha alamr, wqalt: kayf 'aladu wa'ana eajuz eaqim la ald?"
  51,30,"qalt laha malayikat allh: hkdha qal rabuk kama akhbrnak, wahu alqadir ealaa dhlk, fala ejb min qdrth. 'iinah subhanah wteala hu alhakim aldhy yadae al'ashya' mwadeha, alealim bmsalh ebadh"
  51,31,"qal 'iibrahim ealayh alslam, lmlaykt allh: ma shankm wfym 'ursltm? qalu: 'iina allah 'arsalna 'iilaa qawm qad 'ajramuu lkfrhm ballh; lnhlkhm bihijarat min tin mthjjir, mellamt eind rabik lhwla' almtjawzyn alhdd fi alfjwr walesyan"
  51,32,"qal 'iibrahim ealayh alslam, lmlaykt allh: ma shankm wfym 'ursltm? qalu: 'iina allah 'arsalna 'iilaa qawm qad 'ajramuu lkfrhm ballh; lnhlkhm bihijarat min tin mthjjir, mellamt eind rabik lhwla' almtjawzyn alhdd fi alfjwr walesyan"
  51,33,"qal 'iibrahim ealayh alslam, lmlaykt allh: ma shankm wfym 'ursltm? qalu: 'iina allah 'arsalna 'iilaa qawm qad 'ajramuu lkfrhm ballh; lnhlkhm bihijarat min tin mthjjir, mellamt eind rabik lhwla' almtjawzyn alhdd fi alfjwr walesyan"
  51,34,"qal 'iibrahim ealayh alslam, lmlaykt allh: ma shankm wfym 'ursltm? qalu: 'iina allah 'arsalna 'iilaa qawm qad 'ajramuu lkfrhm ballh; lnhlkhm bihijarat min tin mthjjir, mellamt eind rabik lhwla' almtjawzyn alhdd fi alfjwr walesyan"
  51,35,fakhrjna man kan fi qaryat qawm lut min 'ahl al'iyman
  51,36,"fma wajadna fi tilk alqaryat ghayr bayt min almslmyn, wahu bayt lut ealayh alslam"
  51,37,"wtrkna fi alqaryat almadhkurat athrana min aleadhab baqyana elamt ealaa qudrat allah taealaa wantqamh min alkfrt, wdhlk eibratan liman yakhafun eadhab allah almwlm almwje"
  51,38,"wafi 'irsalna musaa 'iilaa fireawn wamalayih bialayat walmejzat alzzahirat ayatan liladhin yakhafun aleadhab alalym. faerad fireawn mghtrrana bqwth wjanbh, waqal ean mwsa: 'iinah sahir 'aw mjnwn"
  51,39,"wfy 'irsalna musaa 'iilaa fireawn wamalayih bialayat walmejzat alzzahirat ayatan liladhin yakhafun aleadhab alalym. faerad fireawn mghtrrana bqwth wjanbh, waqal ean mwsa: 'iinah sahir 'aw mjnwn"
  51,40,"fakhdhna fireawn wjnwdh, ftrhnahm fi albhr, wahu at ma ylam elyh; bsbb kufruh wjhwdh wfjwrh"
  51,41,"wfy shan ead w'ihlakhm ayat waeabr liman taml, 'iidh 'arsalna ealayhim alriyh alty la brkt fiha wala tati bkhyr, ma tadae shyyana mrrat ealayh 'iilaa syarth kalshy' albaly"
  51,42,"wfy shan ead w'ihlakhm ayat waeabr liman taml, 'iidh 'arsalna ealayhim alriyh alty la brkt fiha wala tati bkhyr, ma tadae shyyana mrrat ealayh 'iilaa syarth kalshy' albaly"
  51,43,"wfy shan thamud w'ihlakhm ayat webr, 'iidh qil lhm: antfeu bhyatkm hataa tantahi ajalkm. faeasawa 'amr rbhm, fa'akhadhathum saeiqat aledhab, wahum yanzurun 'iilaa eqwbthm baeynhm"
