  77,38,"hadha yawm yafsil allah fih bayn alkhlayq, wytmyz fih alhaqu min albatl, jamaenakum fih -ya maeshar kafaar hadhih alamt- mae alkufaar al'awalin min al'umam almadyt, fa'iin kan lakum hilatan fi alkhalas min aleadhab fahtalu, wanqdhu 'anfusakum min batsh allah wantqamh"
  77,39,"hdha yawm yafsil allah fih bayn alkhlayq, wytmyz fih alhaqu min albatl, jamaenakum fih -ya maeshar kafaar hadhih alamt- mae alkufaar al'awalin min al'umam almadyt, fa'iin kan lakum hilatan fi alkhalas min aleadhab fahtalu, wanqdhu 'anfusakum min batsh allah wantqamh"
