  81,26,"fayn tadhhab bikum eqwlkm fi altkdhyb bialquran baed hadhih alhujaj alqate? ma hu 'iilaa maweizat min allah lajamie alnas, liman sha' minkum 'an yastaqim ealaa alhaqi wal'iyman, wama tshawwn alastqamt, wala taqdarun ealaa dhlk, 'iilaa bmshyyt allah rabu alkhlayq ajmeyn"
  81,27,"fayn tadhhab bikum eqwlkm fi altkdhyb bialquran baed hadhih alhujaj alqate? ma hu 'iilaa maweizat min allah lajamie alnas, liman sha' minkum 'an yastaqim ealaa alhaqi wal'iyman, wama tshawwn alastqamt, wala taqdarun ealaa dhlk, 'iilaa bmshyyt allah rabu alkhlayq ajmeyn"
  81,28,"fa'ayn tadhhab bikum eqwlkm fi altkdhyb bialquran baed hadhih alhujaj alqate? ma hu 'iilaa maweizat min allah lajamie alnas, liman sha' minkum 'an yastaqim ealaa alhaqi wal'iyman, wama tshawwn alastqamt, wala taqdarun ealaa dhlk, 'iilaa bmshyyt allah rabu alkhlayq ajmeyn"
  81,29,"fayn tadhhab bikum eqwlkm fi altkdhyb bialquran baed hadhih alhujaj alqate? ma hu 'iilaa maweizat min allah lajamie alnas, liman sha' minkum 'an yastaqim ealaa alhaqi wal'iyman, wama tshawwn alastqamt, wala taqdarun ealaa dhlk, 'iilaa bmshyyt allah rabu alkhlayq ajmeyn"
  82,1,"'idha alsama' anshqt, wakhtll nzamha, wa'iidha alkawakib tsaqtt, wa'iidha albihar fjjar allah bedha fi bed, fdhhb mawha, wa'iidha alqubur qulibt bbeth man kan fyha, hinayidh taelam kll nafs jmye aemalha, ma tqddam mnha, wama takhr, wjwzyt bha"
